<br>
Anyway, what are your thoughts on Beastlords on FV? By far the most are Cats, then Barbs, Iksar, Troll and Ogres are few and far between. <br>
<br>
To those of us out there - at level 22 you can go to Upper Guk and solo getting Chitin shell armor (chest slot, AC 17, Sv vrs Poison +10). Upper Guk xp rivals Paludal, but it doesn't flow in as fast, due to the layout of the dungeon. <br>
<br>
Thanks for thoughts!<br>
<br>
