<br>
If'n ya wanna be a raid-typre, ferget it.  Ya depend on yer pet ta do at least half yer damage most of the time and most raid leaders won't let ya call on em.  (Nevermind that they dont agro anythin, ya can have complete control over em and that ya can shrink em so small they aren't in anyone's way.)  Ya can find friends ta hunt with that will appriciate yer talents--like holdin up two mobs while the team slays the third durin a bad pull, or lettin the pet take the nasty spells until the creature uses all its mana.<br>
<br>
Anyway, I hope there are more of us comin up in the world and that we show the doubters what we can do.  *Imagins six beastlords and their warders on a hunt together*  *smile*<br>
<br>
Crowe<br>
